## Goal 
- Understand how attackers discover hidden parts of a website.

-> Before exploiting anything we must know what pages exist on this website,Because many sensitive pages are not linked publicly.
- Example: we visit a website (http://target-site.com) and we see (Home | About | Contact) but the server also contain 
- /admin
- /login
- /uploads
- /dev
- /backup,
and these are not linked anywhere, attackers discover them through enumeration.

